1
03:37:53,712 --> 03:37:55,379
Ironfoot.

2
03:37:57,883 --> 03:37:59,884
[SHOUTING]

3
03:38:06,266 --> 03:38:08,017
[ALL SHOUTING]

4
03:38:08,268 --> 03:38:09,268
[SHOUTS IN ELVISH]

5
03:38:15,525 --> 03:38:19,926
DAIN:
Hey, Thorin! Ironfoot has come!

6
03:38:26,870 --> 03:38:27,995
Who is that?

7
03:38:28,538 --> 03:38:29,788
He doesn't look very happy.

8
03:38:30,040 --> 03:38:32,791
It is Dain, Lord of the Iron Hills.

9
03:38:33,043 --> 03:38:35,753
Thorin's cousin.
- Are they alike?

10
03:38:36,838 --> 03:38:40,466
I've always found Thorin
the more reasonable of the two.

11
03:38:50,727 --> 03:38:51,852
DAIN:
Good morning.

12
03:38:52,103 --> 03:38:53,646
How are we all?

13
03:38:57,234 --> 03:39:02,655
I have a wee proposition if you wouldn't
mind giving me a few moments of your time.

14
03:39:03,907 --> 03:39:05,950
Would you consider...

15
03:39:07,622 --> 03:39:09,203
...just sodding off?

16
03:39:10,538 --> 03:39:11,538
<i>All of you!</i>

17
03:39:11,790 --> 03:39:13,249
<i>Right now!</i>

18
03:39:13,500 --> 03:39:14,500
Stand fast.

19
03:39:16,163 --> 03:39:17,960
Come now, Lord Dain.

20
03:39:18,463 --> 03:39:20,294
Gandalf the Grey.

21
03:39:21,967 --> 03:39:24,368
Tell this rabble to leave...

22
03:39:24,618 --> 03:39:27,096
...or I'll water
the ground with their blood!

23
03:39:30,408 --> 03:39:34,645
There is no need for war
between Dwarves, Men and Elves.

24
03:39:34,896 --> 03:39:38,779
A legion of Orcs march on the Mountain.
Stand your army down.

25
03:39:39,112 --> 03:39:41,944
I will not stand down before any Elf.

26
03:39:42,654 --> 03:39:45,656
Not least this faithless Woodland sprite.

27
03:39:46,658 --> 03:39:49,702
He wishes nothing but ill upon my people.

28
03:39:50,787 --> 03:39:54,707
If he chooses to stand
between me and my kin...

29
03:39:55,677 --> 03:39:57,876
...I'll split his pretty head open!

30
03:40:00,019 --> 03:40:02,047
See if he's still smirking then.

31
03:40:04,259 --> 03:40:06,176
GANDALF:
Dain, wait!

32
03:40:07,554 --> 03:40:09,555
[ALL SHOUTING]

33
03:40:11,442 --> 03:40:12,558
Let them advance.

34
03:40:12,726 --> 03:40:14,560
See how far they get.

35
03:40:14,811 --> 03:40:17,062
DAIN: You think I give a dead dog
for your threats...

36
03:40:17,314 --> 03:40:20,691
...you pointy-eared princess?

37
03:40:21,891 --> 03:40:24,153
You hear that, lads? We're on!

38
03:40:24,446 --> 03:40:27,072
Let's give these bastards
a good hammering!

39
03:40:27,324 --> 03:40:28,824
[SHOUTING IN DWARVISH]

40
03:40:29,701 --> 03:40:31,493
[ALL SHOUTING]

41
03:40:31,828 --> 03:40:32,995
Stand your men down.

42
03:40:33,246 --> 03:40:35,622
I'll deal with Ironfoot and his rabble.

43
03:40:41,796 --> 03:40:44,506
Right then.
Let's get this done.

44
03:40:45,467 --> 03:40:47,092
Send in the goats.

45
03:40:47,427 --> 03:40:49,261
[DWARF SHOUTS IN DWARVISH]

46
03:40:59,064 --> 03:41:00,647
[SHOUTING IN ELVISH]

